        "  - Run 'Firefox Nightly Profile Manager', choose 'Scoop-Nightly' then click 'Start Nightly'.",
        "  - Visit 'about:profiles' page in Firefox Nightly to check *DEFAULT* profile.",
        "For details: https://support.mozilla.org/en-US/kb/profile-manager-create-remove-switch-firefox-profiles"
    ],
    "architecture": {
        "64bit": {
            "url": "https://archive.mozilla.org/pub/firefox/nightly/2026/03/2026-03-15-08-57-00-mozilla-central/firefox-150.0a1.en-US.win64.installer.exe#/dl.7z",
            "hash": "sha512:d6a696a822996217366ac49b155ea9cc8016ed8a9ce1bffb134f1fb60c3e180bb5828c3fba918cbe80debe75b3af6aa5fa5ebfe16f4aa8b1efd3aa11ce3aebfe"
        },
        "32bit": {
            "url": "https://archive.mozilla.org/pub/firefox/nightly/2026/03/2026-03-15-08-57-00-mozilla-central/firefox-150.0a1.en-US.win32.installer.exe#/dl.7z",
